ing-[15px] before:hidden after:hidden dark:bg-[#484848]/30">IoU =3D Interse=
ction Length / Union Length
</code></pre>
<p>Where:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Intersection Length</strong>: Number of overlapping characters =
between predicted and ground truth intervals</li>
<li><strong>Union Length</strong>: Total span covered by both intervals com=
bined</li>
</ul>
<p>An interval pair is considered a match if their IoU exceeds a specific t=
hreshold (e.g., 0.5, 0.75, 0.95).</p>
